pageContext.claim: “As promised, our campaign against the MS-13 gang continues. '@ICEgov Busts 39 MS-13 Members in New York Operation"'”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is indeed ramping up enforcement actions against MS-13, but enforcement action so far is a continuation of Operation Community Shield, which has been going on since 2005. While a recent six-week raid was the biggest raid to date against MS-13 members and associates, there's not been a significant change in deportations yet that Trump promised on the campaign.
